Please forgive me.

820
00:58:17,260 --> 00:58:18,710
Isn't that Noisy Gong?

821
00:58:19,860 --> 00:58:20,910
No.

822
00:58:21,930 --> 00:58:22,980
This woman isn't

823
00:58:23,950 --> 00:58:25,140
Yeon-seo.

824
00:58:27,430 --> 00:58:28,570
Then who is it?

825
00:58:44,980 --> 00:58:47,000
Now you disregard everything
and just break in?

826
00:58:48,940 --> 00:58:50,300
Why did you deceive me?

827
00:58:51,800 --> 00:58:54,660
Are you obsessed with Yeon-seo
because she resembles her?

828
00:58:54,750 --> 00:58:56,200
-Shut up.
-I thought

829
00:59:01,700 --> 00:59:03,640
you were Yeon-seo's missing rib.

830
00:59:04,210 --> 00:59:05,920
I believed you were her destiny.

831
00:59:06,890 --> 00:59:08,960
Once Yeon-seo falls in love with her rib

832
00:59:09,620 --> 00:59:11,070
and finds happiness,

833
00:59:11,910 --> 00:59:14,590
I thought I could return
to paradise in peace.

834
00:59:14,990 --> 00:59:16,620
Like I said, I'll do that.

835
00:59:17,670 --> 00:59:20,050
Everything is settled. Mission success.

836
00:59:20,140 --> 00:59:21,630
No, I don't need you.

837
00:59:22,600 --> 00:59:23,830
You're out.

838
00:59:24,670 --> 00:59:26,960
I waited to tell you that the one

839
00:59:27,920 --> 00:59:30,520
who should stop lurking around her
is you, not me.

840
00:59:31,270 --> 00:59:33,470
Listen to the angel's order

841
00:59:34,390 --> 00:59:35,400
and obey.

842
00:59:39,010 --> 00:59:40,290
So what will you do now?

843
00:59:41,780 --> 00:59:42,880
Are you

844
00:59:44,120 --> 00:59:45,700
going to be her rib?

845
00:59:45,790 --> 00:59:47,150
It's none of your business.

846
00:59:47,640 --> 00:59:49,440
If I turn into dust or dissipate,

847
00:59:49,750 --> 00:59:51,200
that's for me to deal with.

848
00:59:57,540 --> 00:59:59,210
You'll be very lucky
if you just dissipate.

849
00:59:59,300 --> 01:00:01,450
You can't even imagine
what the punishment is like.

850
01:00:01,540 --> 01:00:04,400
Something horrifying will happen.

851
01:00:08,580 --> 01:00:09,640
He'll come.

852
01:00:12,230 --> 01:00:13,380
He won't come.

853
01:00:14,390 --> 01:00:15,490
He'll come.

854
01:00:17,120 --> 01:00:18,220
He won't come.

855
01:00:18,350 --> 01:00:21,430
What is this? Forget it. This is no fun.

856
01:00:22,000 --> 01:00:24,110
I'll start with "He won't come."
He won't come.

857
01:00:25,520 --> 01:00:26,570
He won't come.

858
01:00:27,540 --> 01:00:28,600
He'll come.

859
01:00:30,360 --> 01:00:31,370
He won't come.

860
01:00:32,290 --> 01:00:33,790
Darn it, these flowers.

861
01:00:53,150 --> 01:00:54,210
You're here.

862
01:00:55,830 --> 01:00:57,020
I'm sorry I'm late.

863
01:01:02,520 --> 01:01:04,770
Is everything finished?

864
01:01:06,750 --> 01:01:08,330
You won't leave again, will you?

865
01:01:10,930 --> 01:01:12,990
If you say that you'll quit again

866
01:01:13,300 --> 01:01:14,890
or disappear without telling me,

867
01:01:15,550 --> 01:01:17,570
I'll kill you. Okay?

868
01:01:20,470 --> 01:01:22,190
You can't get sick
without telling me either.

869
01:01:23,380 --> 01:01:25,090
You can't die when I'm not around either.

870
01:01:26,460 --> 01:01:27,470
Okay?

871
01:01:30,420 --> 01:01:32,270
Why won't you say anything?

872
01:01:33,630 --> 01:01:34,730
Promise me.

873
01:01:41,990 --> 01:01:44,230
(You can't even imagine
what the punishment is like.)

874
01:01:44,320 --> 01:01:47,270
(Something horrifying will happen.)

875
01:01:49,650 --> 01:01:50,700
I love you.

876
01:01:54,040 --> 01:01:55,100
I love you.

877
01:01:56,380 --> 01:01:57,430
Lee Yeon-seo.

878
01:02:51,600 --> 01:02:54,940
(Angel's Last Mission: Love)

879
01:02:56,660 --> 01:02:58,550
(It's not a crime to love a lot,)

880
01:02:58,860 --> 01:03:00,480
but it's a crime to have too many secrets.

881
01:03:00,620 --> 01:03:01,760
(Hey, Yeon-seo!)

882
01:03:02,860 --> 01:03:04,000
Young Lady.

883
01:03:04,220 --> 01:03:05,320
Goodness! Ms. Jung!

884
01:03:06,160 --> 01:03:09,370
(Yeon-seo. Listen carefully
to what I'm about to tell you.)

885
01:03:10,030 --> 01:03:12,060
Do you know what a guardian angel is?

886
01:03:12,850 --> 01:03:16,150
(The best thing you can do for her
at this point is leaving.)

887
01:03:16,720 --> 01:03:20,110
(I'm sure there is a way for an angel
to become a human.)

888
01:03:20,200 --> 01:03:23,670
(I wish Yeon-seo was dead.)

889
01:03:23,760 --> 01:03:24,730
(Yeon-seo!)
